Author: Suzanne Harwood
Content:
I wish I had known this tool a few years earlier. I was physically much sicker and much weaker than I am today and I know now that demons had taken ahold of me — I had a looping video constantly going through my head of killing myself. I was watching the how, where, and the immediate aftermath. It was incessant. I once even heard a very deep dark voice speaking to me (incoherently) for just a few seconds. I went to a psychologist who helped me get through it. 
Looking back, I really do think it was a demon trying to take my soul down the deepest, darkest path, because this way of thinking is very unlike me!!!
